      property title =
         "Architecture ID";
      property description =
         "The marchid CSR is a 64 bit read-only register encoding the base "
         "microarchitecture of the hart.  The combination of mvendorid and "
         "marchid should uniquely identify the type of hart "
         "microarchitecture that is implemented. For more information, "
